    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/27d3d21c6ee97d97f80d0c6575b6d64c.avif?t=1758712920\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras_big/27d3d21c6ee97d97f80d0c6575b6d64c.avif?t=1758712920 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Synopsis:</strong> Control your ship to destroy incoming enemies to prevent them from damaging your ship or getting past you! Survive incoming waves of enemy ships, unlock more levels as you progress, enhance your weapons by spending gained credits and use powerful temporary powerups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/2ef2d32a4c2399cc10e5dd0cfd5fce09.webp?t=1758712920\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Between levels <strong>UPGRADE</strong> your weapons' systems. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/2ef2d32a4c2399cc10e5dd0cfd5fce09.webp?t=1758712920\" width=16 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/c8e781512023fa05de80152690ed39c0.poster.avif?t=1758712920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/c8e781512023fa05de80152690ed39c0.webm?t=1758712920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/c8e781512023fa05de80152690ed39c0.mp4?t=1758712920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/2ef2d32a4c2399cc10e5dd0cfd5fce09.webp?t=1758712920\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Pick up temporary <strong>POWERUPS</strong> dropped by slain enemies. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/2ef2d32a4c2399cc10e5dd0cfd5fce09.webp?t=1758712920\" width=16 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/bbaeb1c0f6d85752aad52839e2b8ad83.poster.avif?t=1758712920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/bbaeb1c0f6d85752aad52839e2b8ad83.webm?t=1758712920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/bbaeb1c0f6d85752aad52839e2b8ad83.mp4?t=1758712920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/2ef2d32a4c2399cc10e5dd0cfd5fce09.webp?t=1758712920\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Unlock more <strong>LEVELS</strong> as you progress. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/2ef2d32a4c2399cc10e5dd0cfd5fce09.webp?t=1758712920\" width=16 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/af69f7fd22be926ab2370705af5b9dca.poster.avif?t=1758712920\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/af69f7fd22be926ab2370705af5b9dca.webm?t=1758712920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246970/extras/af69f7fd22be926ab2370705af5b9dca.mp4?t=1758712920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradable weapons stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Temporary powerups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements.</p></li></ul>",
